Valid bundle for an in-toto DSSE envelope, logged to a Rekor v2 instance
using the new "hashedrekord-over-DSSE" encoding (rekor-v2-spec §6.1.4):
the tlog entry is kind=hashedrekord/0.0.2 and stores
Hash(PAE(payloadType, payload)) instead of the full envelope.

Signed against staging Sigstore (staging Fulcio, staging Rekor v2) using
the sigstore-conformance/extremely-dangerous-public-oidc-beacon workflow
identity. The bundle ships its own trusted_root.json (the staging trust
root); once production has a Rekor v2 instance the custom trust root can
be removed.
